{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) PCR_Init:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~aik ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> PCR_Init( &#39;pcr0&#39;, ~aik ), UniqueInit( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> PCR( &#39;pcr0&#39; ), !AIK( ~aik ), Out( pk(~aik) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) PCR_Extend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> PCR( x ), In( y ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> PCR_Extend( x, y, h(&lt;x, y&gt;) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> PCR( h(&lt;x, y&gt;) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [0]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) PCR_CreateKey:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~ska ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KeyTable( h(&lt;&#39;pcr0&#39;, $a&gt;), ~ska ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) PCR_CertKey:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !AIK( aik ), !KeyTable( x, sk ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> PCR_CertKey_Inst( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( sign(&lt;&#39;certkey&#39;, x, pk(sk)&gt;, aik) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) PCR_Unbind:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> PCR( x ), !KeyTable( x, sk ), In( aenc(m, pk(sk)) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> PCR_Unbind( x, sk, m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> PCR( x ), Out( m ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [0]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Alice_Init:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Fr( ~s0 ), Fr( ~s1 ), !AIK( aik ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( sign(&lt;&#39;certkey&#39;, x0, pk0&gt;, aik) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( sign(&lt;&#39;certkey&#39;, x1, pk1&gt;, aik) )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> InEq( x0, x1 ), Secrets( ~s0, ~s1 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( aenc(~s0, pk0) ), Out( aenc(~s1, pk1) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> UniqueInit_unique:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>UniqueInit( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>UniqueInit( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>UniqueInit( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>UniqueInit( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> Ineq_checks_succeed:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>t #e<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>InEq( t, t ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #e<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">⊥</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>t #e<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>InEq( t, t ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #e<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">⊥</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}